Package io.ib67.astralflow.item.oredict

Interface IOreDict

@AvailableSince("0.1.0") @Internal public interface IOreDict
An ore dictionary, where you can register same name for more items
You should consider using ItemBuilder instead of this class. This class may cause misleading and not very easy to understand.
